pa que perdió a su hijo, pero Victoria se contuvo; Nicolás está sorprendido. El último secreto que revela Florencia es que el verdadero asesino de Jaimito del Casal es Rosendo Zapata." type="episode" contentRating="NONADULT" duration="2505000" grandparentArt="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1080/3/1766385.jpg" grandparentGuid="plex://show/67a0b759cb3d68c83b1e7d4f" grandparentKey="/library/metadata/67a0b759cb3d68c83b1e7d4f" grandparentRatingKey="67a0b759cb3d68c83b1e7d4f" grandparentThumb="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1920/2/1766385.jpg" grandparentTitle="La Trepadora" grandparentType="show" index="128" parentIndex="1" requiresConsent="1" skipParent="1" thumb="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1080/3/1766385.jpg" title="S01:E128" userState="0"><Image alt="S01:E128" type="coverArt" url="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1080/3/1766385.jpg"/><Image alt="S01:E128" type="coverPoster" url="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1920/2/1766385.jpg"/><Image alt="S01:E128" type="snapshot" url="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1080/3/1766385.jpg"/><Genre filter="genre=6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" id="6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" key="/library/sections/home/all?genre=6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" ratingKey="genre_6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" slug="drama" tag="Drama" type="directory" context="tag.genre"/><Media beginsAt="1776069396" duration="2505000" endsAt="1776071901" id="69d4510f09c23231cbeef998" onAir="0" premiere="0" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"/><Media beginsAt="1776099288" duration="3044000" endsAt="1776102332" id="69d4510f09c23231cbeef9a2" onAir="0" premiere="0" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"/></Video></MediaContainer>
